textBox.richText: I don’t have many vids that make people go liek OMFG THAT IS AMAZING. But if anything would do it, it’s this one. Multiplayer is something that people have been dying to see in the games, and here’s what it would look like! This actually has four VBAs linked to each other, two set to arrow keys and the other two set to WASD controls. It’s pretty cool!
